A 25-year-old lady, Lilian Onyinyechukwu Nwabuike, on Friday was been laid to rest after she was hit by a stray bullet during the gunmen attack in Agulu, Anaocha Local Government Area of Anambra State. According to reports gathered, Nwabuike was getting ready for her traditional and white wedding ceremonies which were scheduled for next week. Recall that there was a shoot-out on 30, April 2022 between security operatives and gunmen at the military post close to the residence of former Minister of Information, late Prof Dora Akunyili. -Advertisement- It was reported that three of the gunmen were killed while others sustained bullet wounds.